1
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:35,920
It's done.

2
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,040
Master,

3
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,719
we got her.

4
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:40,319
Good.

5
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,519
Good.

6
00:01:45,319 --> 00:01:46,480
Do you know what this is called?

7
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,680
This is karma coming due.

8
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,239
My dear third brother

9
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:54,200
could be cruel enough

10
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:56,079
to ruin his own brother's future.

11
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,799
Then don't blame me

12
00:01:57,799 --> 00:02:00,040
for making him taste the torment

13
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:02,079
of losing his beloved.

14
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,120
But Master,

15
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,799
that man Xie said

16
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,400
he couldn't get out.

17
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,400
He had no choice

18
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:10,159
but to hide in the capital for now.

19
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,159
What?

20
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,439
This...

21
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,800
What... what else did he say?

22
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:17,439
He said...

23
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,800
losing his beloved

24
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,919
is agony beyond bearing.

25
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:25,319
Third Uncle's beloved...

26
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:28,560
Everyone in the manor is still there.

27
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,400
Could it be Gu Jinzhao?

28
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,719
For the next two days,

29
00:02:35,159 --> 00:02:36,120
do nothing else.

30
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,479
Keep an eye on Fourth Uncle.

31
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:39,680
No.

32
00:02:41,919 --> 00:02:43,199
He won't show himself.

33
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,400
Watch that Chen Zhong.

34
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,800
See what he does next.

35
00:02:54,039 --> 00:02:54,599
Yah!

36
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,400
Mr. Jiang sent word.

37
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,120
They found traces of the villains.

38
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,439
They seemingly headed for the capital.

39
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,319
You just
lock them in there?

40
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,400
With people coming and going,

41
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,759
what if someone finds out?

42
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,759
You don't understand.

43
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,759
The darkest place is under the lamp.

44
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:37,960
Don't worry.

45
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,039
Tomorrow morning,

46
00:03:39,319 --> 00:03:40,960
the trafficker will come inspect the goods.

47
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,639
Once they're in his hands,

48
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,360
there are plenty of ways

49
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:46,159
to erase her trail.

50
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:52,800
Chen Yi.

51
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,120
Take my card

52
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,000
to the City Garrison.

53
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,039
Tell them I'll be there shortly.

54
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:56,719
And...
Fetch my seal from home.

55
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:58,039
Hurry.
Yes.

56
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:00,240
Sir.

57
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:01,520
Are you going to...
Seal up the city.

58
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:03,719
Since she's in the city,

59
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,639
lock the capital down for me.

60
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,639
Shut the gates and search.

61
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,080
I'll take both.

62
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,040
Forty taels of silver.

63
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,279
Not a coin more.

64
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:49,079
Follow him.

65
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,199
What are you doing?
Let us go!

66
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:03,800
Brother.

67
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,560
Give me some water.

68
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,120
So much nonsense.

69
00:05:28,399 --> 00:05:29,240
Then don't eat.
Sir, sir.

70
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,959
This is truly awful.

71
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,160
I can't swallow it.

72
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,360
How about this?

73
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,639
Take this thing
off my wrist.

74
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,319
Take this to a pawnshop.

75
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,480
It'll fetch at least a hundred taels.

76
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:02,839
Look. What is this?

77
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,519
You've done well.

78
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,319
Of course.

79
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,759
Hold it.

80
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,040
Seize this woman
for me.

81
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:23,800
You...

82
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,399
You...

83
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,879
What are you doing? You...

84
00:06:28,519 --> 00:06:29,720
This pink pearl

85
00:06:29,839 --> 00:06:31,120
was brought back from the Western Sea.

86
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,600
In the capital, there's only this one.

87
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:34,920
It was given by our Old Madam
as part of the dowry

88
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,720
for my young lady.

89
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:37,519
Speak up.

90
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,360
How did it get into your hands?

91
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,240
I...

92
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:44,079
I don't know.

93
00:06:46,839 --> 00:06:47,360
Nanny.

94
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,560
This is the gentleman.

95
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,040
Stand down.

96
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,920
I hear

97
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:59,120
you want one with fine looks,

98
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,959
one who can read and write,

99
00:07:02,319 --> 00:07:05,079
and from a good family too.

100
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,319
Goods like that

101
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,720
do exist.

102
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,720
But

103
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:12,600
they won't come cheap.

104
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,839
Name your price.

105
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:18,560
Two hundred taels, then.

106
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:28,639
Why is there only one hundred fifty?

107
00:07:33,279 --> 00:07:34,279
This jade pendant of mine

108
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,639
is worth fifty taels at least.

109
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:39,360
But

110
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,439
you must let me see the girl first.

111
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,800
Then I'll give it to you.

112
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,879
You want to inspect the goods?

113
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,279
Fine.

114
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:49,279
Then come with me.

115
00:07:58,319 --> 00:08:00,160
She's inside.

116
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,399
Go on.

117
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:19,160
By now,

118
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,720
she has been drugged.

119
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,120
When you take her away later,

120
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,360
the road will be easier.

121
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:28,000
The drug will do her no harm.

122
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:00,279
Step aside.

123
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,600
[Third Uncle's voice.]

124
00:09:11,919 --> 00:09:12,639
Don't run.

125
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:36,759
Don't move.

126
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,679
It's all right now.

127
00:10:21,639 --> 00:10:22,480
- Yanyun
- It's all right.

128
00:10:24,559 --> 00:10:25,799
You scared me to death.

129
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,519
It's all right.

130
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,159
It's all right. It's over.

131
00:10:36,759 --> 00:10:37,440
Are you okay?

132
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,279
Yanyun.

133
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:46,720
Jinzhao. Jinzhao.

134
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:02,879
Stop!

135
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:04,679
Stop!

136
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:09,679
Don't pull me.

137
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:14,519
Get away.

138
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,879
Then perish!

139
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:17,600
Perish!

140
00:11:39,919 --> 00:11:40,639
Young master.

141
00:11:43,440 --> 00:11:44,679
She saw our faces.

142
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:47,120
I know.

143
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:02,720
Young master.

144
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:03,960
Don't be afraid.

145
00:12:06,879 --> 00:12:08,200
Yunting killed him.

146
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:10,759
Don't be afraid.

147
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,279
Don't be afraid, young master.

148
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:28,320
Gu Jinzhao was abducted by thugs?

149
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:29,080
Yes.

150
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,600
In his panic, Lord Chen

151
00:12:30,759 --> 00:12:31,799
called the Five City Garrison.

152
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,279
All city gates were locked.

153
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,360
They claimed they were hunting bandits

154
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,600
and searched house by house.

155
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,600
In the end, she was found

156
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:39,759
in a house in the south city.

157
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:55,960
So this is the man you chose, Gu Jinzhao.

158
00:13:01,159 --> 00:13:01,720
You.

159
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,360
Take a few men.

160
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:05,960
Take my warrant with you

161
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:08,200
to the City Garrison.

162
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,919
Bring back the thugs

163
00:13:09,919 --> 00:13:11,000
who kidnapped Gu Jinzhao.

164
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,039
Tell them this case

165
00:13:13,519 --> 00:13:14,720
falls to the Xuanfeng Guard.

166
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,320
Yes.

167
00:13:19,759 --> 00:13:21,000
Bring out the prisoners

168
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:21,759
caught yesterday.
Yes.

169
00:13:25,759 --> 00:13:26,360
My lord.

170
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,679
You needn't follow.

171
00:13:34,519 --> 00:13:36,720
Why is she not back yet?

172
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,159
Hupo.

173
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:39,679
Go check at the gate.

174
00:13:39,919 --> 00:13:40,440
Yes.

175
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,600
Mother.

176
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:43,960
Shall we go back

177
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,159
and wait inside?

178
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,200
Tell me,

179
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:49,639
Jinzhao is far too willful.

180
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,559
When a bride returns home,

181
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:53,000
who doesn't go to her father's family?

182
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,159
But she...

183
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,039
She insisted on her mother's family.

184
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:57,679
Look now.

185
00:13:58,159 --> 00:13:59,080
Trouble came, didn't it?

186
00:13:59,399 --> 00:14:01,360
Mother, calm yourself.

187
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,000
Jinzhao

188
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,519
was indeed a little willful.

189
00:14:05,159 --> 00:14:05,799
But
she didn't know

190
00:14:06,559 --> 00:14:08,080
she would be abducted.

191
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,360
At least she was saved.

192
00:14:10,519 --> 00:14:11,240
Wasn't she?

193
00:14:12,039 --> 00:14:12,919
But still,

194
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:15,039
she was missing all day and night.

195
00:14:15,679 --> 00:14:17,240
Who knows what happened?

196
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,000
And she is a Grand Secretary's wife, no less.

197
00:14:21,519 --> 00:14:22,440
From now on,

198
00:14:22,759 --> 00:14:24,679
the gossip won't be light.

199
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:27,480
That's exactly what I fear.

200
00:14:27,799 --> 00:14:29,320
If tongues wag about her,

201
00:14:30,759 --> 00:14:32,759
Yanyun will be dragged into it too.

202
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,440
Honestly.

203
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:45,240
My lord.

204
00:14:45,519 --> 00:14:46,360
How is it?

205
00:14:46,799 --> 00:14:47,679
All of them were caught.

206
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,159
I took a shortcut
back to report to you.

207
00:14:50,799 --> 00:14:51,440
My lord,

208
00:14:51,679 --> 00:14:53,000
before Mr. Chen traces this to us,

209
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,159
we should run.

210
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:55,759
If we don't leave now,

211
00:14:56,559 --> 00:14:57,399
it'll be too late.
It's over.

212
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:00,360
It's all over now.

213
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,039
They're here.

214
00:15:02,399 --> 00:15:03,360
They're here. They're here.

215
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,000
My lord.

216
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:08,960
Third Madam is back.
Should we go too?

217
00:15:11,879 --> 00:15:12,720
You go.

218
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:13,639
My lord.

219
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:15,559
I need to go out.

220
00:15:15,879 --> 00:15:17,120
Go out? Where?

221
00:15:17,759 --> 00:15:19,000
Chen Zhong just sent word.

222
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,039
The Southern Office

223
00:15:20,039 --> 00:15:21,600
will add two million salt permits next month.

224
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,120
I must go at once.

225
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,519
Chen Zhong, prepare the carriage.

226
00:15:25,759 --> 00:15:26,639
Yes, Master.

227
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:29,600
Wait.

228
00:15:29,759 --> 00:15:30,879
Need it be so urgent?

229
00:15:31,080 --> 00:15:32,279
Can't you leave tomorrow morning?

230
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,039
What do you know?

231
00:15:51,519 --> 00:15:52,120
Mother.
This...

232
00:15:53,279 --> 00:15:53,759
This...

233
00:15:55,799 --> 00:15:56,960
You should put me down.

234
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:57,840
I can walk myself.

235
00:15:59,000 --> 00:15:59,679
Mother.

236
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,879
Jinzhao was frightened just now

237
00:16:01,879 --> 00:16:02,639
and sprained her ankle.

238
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,039
I'll take her back.

239
00:16:06,159 --> 00:16:07,080
Go back, then.

240
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,399
Yunting.

241
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,519
Young master.

242
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,240
Do you think

243
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:20,000
I look like a joke?

244
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:29,720
Who does such a thing?

245
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,559
How shameless.

246
00:16:32,159 --> 00:16:32,879
Mother.

247
00:16:33,519 --> 00:16:34,440
Yanyun

248
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:36,279
is clearly doing it on purpose.

249
00:16:36,639 --> 00:16:37,679
On purpose?

250
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:40,080
This is at home.

251
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:42,000
Does he need so many schemes?

252
00:16:42,399 --> 00:16:43,320
Honestly.

253
00:16:44,519 --> 00:16:46,440
A good man has been led astray.

254
00:16:50,159 --> 00:16:51,279
About what happened today,

255
00:16:51,919 --> 00:16:54,519
no one is to mention it again.

256
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:55,840
Yes.

257
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,840
If anyone

258
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:00,720
dares wag their tongue

259
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,759
and I hear of it,

260
00:17:03,559 --> 00:17:04,519
no trial needed.

261
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,200
Beat them dead where they stand.

262
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:08,519
Yes, yes.

263
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,920
It's getting late.

264
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,359
All of you may leave.

265
00:17:23,319 --> 00:17:23,920
Will you sit?

266
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,200
I'll take off your shoes.

267
00:17:32,119 --> 00:17:32,880
How is it?

268
00:17:33,559 --> 00:17:34,640
You were wronged today.

269
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,920
This time you were abducted.

270
00:17:37,759 --> 00:17:39,200
People will inevitably gossip.

271
00:17:39,799 --> 00:17:41,240
By carrying you in like this,

272
00:17:42,319 --> 00:17:43,960
if any blind fools still dare,

273
00:17:44,559 --> 00:17:45,359
then don't blame me

274
00:17:45,359 --> 00:17:46,559
Let no one say I gave no warning.

275
00:17:46,759 --> 00:17:47,359
Sir.

276
00:17:54,079 --> 00:17:55,200
I'll be back soon.

277
00:17:59,599 --> 00:18:00,240
Miss.

278
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,119
Let me help you bathe.

279
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:04,680
Let Nanny Zhao do it.

280
00:18:05,519 --> 00:18:06,720
Go back and rest.

281
00:18:07,279 --> 00:18:08,599
If anything feels wrong,

282
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:09,720
tell me.
I'm fine.

283
00:18:11,079 --> 00:18:11,920
It's nothing.

284
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:16,319
Listen to Miss.

285
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,279
Go back and rest.
I'm here.

286
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:19,319
It's all right, Nanny Zhao.

287
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,200
We'll do it together.

288
00:18:28,720 --> 00:18:30,279
I have urgent matters to handle.

289
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,519
Let them wash you properly

290
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:33,640
and get some real sleep.

291
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:34,960
Don't wait for me.

292
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:37,160
I'll be right back, all right?

293
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:46,680
I'll be right back.

294
00:18:49,359 --> 00:18:50,200
Take good care of Madam.

295
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:51,240
Yes.

296
00:19:02,359 --> 00:19:03,640
I warned you.

297
00:19:04,319 --> 00:19:05,960
Yet again and again, you went too far.

298
00:19:07,119 --> 00:19:07,720
This time, you even

299
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:09,079
laid hands on your sister-in-law.

300
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,440
Because I hate you.

301
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,079
Because I hate you.

302
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:16,519
Why?

303
00:19:17,079 --> 00:19:17,880
Why?

304
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,400
Just because I killed Fifth Brother?

305
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,359
But I barely know nothing then.

306
00:19:22,359 --> 00:19:23,880
I was just a child.

307
00:19:24,319 --> 00:19:25,519
I'm your blood brother.

308
00:19:25,519 --> 00:19:26,440
You could have taught me.

309
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:28,480
Why did you ruin my future?

310
00:19:29,559 --> 00:19:31,000
I also studied ten hard years.

311
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,359
Now I can only manage petty affairs.

312
00:19:32,359 --> 00:19:34,160
Do you know how much I hate you?

313
00:19:37,119 --> 00:19:37,720
So you know

314
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:38,920
you killed Fifth Brother.

315
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:40,640
You brought it on yourself.

316
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:42,519
I brought it on myself?

317
00:19:42,559 --> 00:19:43,880
I brought it on myself?

318
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:48,039
Chen Yanyun, I brought it on myself?

319
00:19:49,359 --> 00:19:50,000
No.

320
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:53,279
You were jealous of me.

321
00:19:53,839 --> 00:19:54,400
You were jealous

322
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:56,079
that Mother loved only me since childhood.

323
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:59,279
So you ruined my whole life.

324
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:02,160
I won't let you live well either.

325
00:20:03,359 --> 00:20:05,559
I'll make you taste my pain.

326
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:07,519
Pain worse than death.

327
00:20:09,279 --> 00:20:09,880
I knew it

328
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:11,400
when I saw the way you looked at that woman.

329
00:20:11,519 --> 00:20:12,079
I knew

330
00:20:12,079 --> 00:20:13,720
that woman is your weak spot.

331
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:15,839
I wanted something to happen to her.

332
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,119
I wanted to abduct her.

333
00:20:18,119 --> 00:20:19,319
I wanted to sell her to a brothel.

334
00:20:19,319 --> 00:20:21,640
I wanted her trampled by the whole world.

335
00:20:35,599 --> 00:20:37,039
With all your crimes,

336
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:39,079
exile to the far frontier would be fitting.

337
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:41,119
Go to Shaanxi. Find Second Brother.

338
00:20:42,079 --> 00:20:43,559
I have written to him

339
00:20:43,559 --> 00:20:44,920
about all you have done.

340
00:20:45,519 --> 00:20:46,720
He will deal with you.

341
00:20:47,519 --> 00:20:48,759
Your children and wife are innocent.

342
00:20:49,640 --> 00:20:50,880
The family will look after them.

343
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:54,519
Chen Yanyun!

344
00:21:00,519 --> 00:21:01,599
Chen Yanyun!

345
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,359
Go sleep in the study.

346
00:21:31,599 --> 00:21:32,400
Are you angry with me?

347
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:33,359
Yes, I am.

348
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:35,160
Leave at once.

349
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:36,279
I don't want to see you.

350
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:38,839
Don't talk to me.
I'm going to bed.

351
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:40,279
I won't go.

352
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:43,000
If I leave,

353
00:21:43,799 --> 00:21:45,160
I'm afraid you won't let me back in.

354
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:47,279
You are a Grand Secretary.

355
00:21:47,519 --> 00:21:48,319
And you're afraid of that?

356
00:21:48,759 --> 00:21:49,359
Yes.

357
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:53,000
A grand Secretary fears nothing.

358
00:21:53,519 --> 00:21:54,680
Except this.

359
00:21:55,279 --> 00:21:56,799
Where did you learn such words?

360
00:21:57,599 --> 00:21:58,519
Wenyuan Pavilion?

361
00:21:58,960 --> 00:21:59,960
I learned quite a lot.

362
00:22:05,039 --> 00:22:06,720
All right, all right.

363
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:11,039
I said I'm sorry, okay?

364
00:22:13,799 --> 00:22:14,880
Just now,

365
00:22:15,839 --> 00:22:17,440
I sent Fourth Brother to Shaanxi.

366
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,680
He likely won't return.

367
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,079
Why?

368
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:22,559
The kidnappers who took you

369
00:22:22,559 --> 00:22:23,599
were bought by him.

370
00:22:24,319 --> 00:22:25,200
To get revenge on me.

371
00:22:26,079 --> 00:22:27,240
He put in quite some effort.

372
00:22:31,279 --> 00:22:32,640
Why would he do that?

373
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,240
It's a long story.

374
00:22:37,079 --> 00:22:38,079
Do you still remember

375
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,240
that I had

376
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:40,960
a late fifth brother?

377
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:43,319
At six, he fell into water by accident.

378
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:45,319
But many years later,
I learned

379
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:47,400
he had not fallen by accident.

380
00:22:47,599 --> 00:22:49,119
Fourth Brother pushed him in.

381
00:22:52,759 --> 00:22:53,519
So

382
00:22:53,920 --> 00:22:55,200
I cut off his imperial exam path

383
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:56,240
and barred him from the exams.

384
00:22:57,079 --> 00:22:58,079
But by then,

385
00:22:58,359 --> 00:22:59,279
he had passed the provincial exam.

386
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,559
So he hated me to the bone.

387
00:23:03,119 --> 00:23:03,839
If

388
00:23:04,079 --> 00:23:05,359
I had known earlier

389
00:23:05,519 --> 00:23:06,839
that he would turn his revenge on you,

390
00:23:08,279 --> 00:23:09,000
I would have...

391
00:23:10,759 --> 00:23:11,559
Would have what?

392
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:13,400
I would have been far harsher.

393
00:23:15,799 --> 00:23:17,759
But if he suddenly disappeared,

394
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:19,519
and Mother learns of it,

395
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:20,759
won't it be hard to explain?

396
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,519
At home, just say

397
00:23:27,079 --> 00:23:27,839
Fourth Brother has gone

398
00:23:27,839 --> 00:23:29,359
to Shaanxi for business.

399
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,039
Rest well

400
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:33,240
these next few days.

401
00:23:34,920 --> 00:23:36,279
No need to pay respects to Mother.

402
00:23:36,519 --> 00:23:37,519
I'll tell her

403
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:38,599
you are unwell.

404
00:23:39,119 --> 00:23:40,680
You're making decisions for me again.

405
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:43,839
Linxia House is about to reopen.

406
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:44,720
I was thinking

407
00:23:44,839 --> 00:23:46,759
I should go take a look tomorrow.

408
00:23:48,720 --> 00:23:49,559
I know

409
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:52,000
you worry that Mother and Sister-in-law

410
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:53,200
will question me endlessly.

411
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:55,799
But I have nothing to hide.

412
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:58,279
Rather than avoiding some things,

413
00:23:58,799 --> 00:23:59,640
it's better

414
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:01,079
to face them openly.

415
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:05,640
All right.

416
00:24:08,559 --> 00:24:09,319
Tomorrow morning,
I'll go with you

417
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,319
to greet Mother.

418
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:12,880
I'll tell her beforehand.

419
00:24:13,279 --> 00:24:14,000
Otherwise,

420
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,759
she may not let you out again.

421
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,319
You mustn't go.

422
00:24:19,559 --> 00:24:20,400
That would make it seem

423
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,599
I borrowed your power

424
00:24:22,079 --> 00:24:23,640
to force her to agree.

425
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:24,839
When the time comes,

426
00:24:24,839 --> 00:24:26,440
even if she agrees on the surface,

427
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,599
she'll still blame me in her heart.

428
00:24:30,599 --> 00:24:31,720
I have my own way.

429
00:24:35,039 --> 00:24:36,519
All right, all right.

430
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:37,920
As my lady commands.

431
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:40,519
It is late.

432
00:24:41,599 --> 00:24:42,440
So now,

433
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,200
shall we sleep?

434
00:24:46,839 --> 00:24:47,279
Come.

435
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,640
Fourth Brother too...

436
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:01,799
He left just like that.

437
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,319
What business is it?

438
00:25:03,519 --> 00:25:04,680
The roads are so far,

439
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:06,240
yet he took no one with him.

440
00:25:07,039 --> 00:25:08,680
I said I would go care for him,

441
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:10,079
but my lord refused.

442
00:25:10,279 --> 00:25:11,039
He said this time

443
00:25:11,039 --> 00:25:12,519
he must go toward Yulin Pass too.

444
00:25:12,799 --> 00:25:13,720
It would be too hard.

445
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:15,200
Yanwen

446
00:25:15,359 --> 00:25:16,960
must have learned from Yanyun.

447
00:25:17,359 --> 00:25:18,799
He has learned to cherish his wife.

448
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:21,279
Yanyun

449
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:24,319
cherishes his rather too much.

450
00:25:25,839 --> 00:25:26,880
Third Madam is here.

451
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:35,160
Greetings, Mother.

452
00:25:36,519 --> 00:25:37,240
Sit.

453
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,640
Have you recovered?

454
00:25:40,079 --> 00:25:41,440
Thank you for your concern, Mother.

455
00:25:41,799 --> 00:25:42,960
I am well now.

456
00:25:49,279 --> 00:25:50,240
Where is Yanyun?

457
00:25:50,519 --> 00:25:51,440
He went early this morning

458
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:52,559
to Wenyuan Pavilion.

459
00:25:54,359 --> 00:25:55,839
So he has returned to Wenyuan Pavilion

460
00:25:56,079 --> 00:25:57,160
to handle affairs?

461
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:58,559
Yes.

462
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,039
Then

463
00:26:01,039 --> 00:26:02,519
that is good.

464
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:04,119
Yanyun

465
00:26:04,279 --> 00:26:06,279
has regained his post as Grand Secretary.

466
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:08,559
As a Grand Secretary's wife,

467
00:26:09,559 --> 00:26:11,000
inside and outside the household,

468
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:13,519
you should conduct yourself properly.

469
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:15,799
Yes.

470
00:26:17,039 --> 00:26:18,000
By the way, Mother.

471
00:26:23,599 --> 00:26:24,880
Linxia House under my name

472
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:26,160
is preparing to reopen.

473
00:26:26,599 --> 00:26:27,839
So I asked the cooks

474
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:28,640
to make some

475
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,000
new styles of pastries.

476
00:26:30,599 --> 00:26:31,519
Early this morning,

477
00:26:31,599 --> 00:26:33,440
I had them prepared and sent here.

478
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:34,519
I hope Mother
and Second Sister-in-law

479
00:26:35,799 --> 00:26:37,680
will let everyone try something fresh.

480
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:40,839
How very thoughtful, Jinzhao.

481
00:26:41,279 --> 00:26:42,920
Linxia House pastries

482
00:26:43,039 --> 00:26:44,039
must be fine, of course.

483
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,759
Only,

484
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:47,240
for us, they would have been enough.

485
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:48,960
You may not know,

486
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:50,759
she never takes sweets.

487
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:53,759
Second Sister-in-law is right.

488
00:26:54,319 --> 00:26:55,319
My grandmother

489
00:26:55,519 --> 00:26:56,920
reminded me long ago.

490
00:26:57,279 --> 00:26:59,079
She said Mother has diabetes

491
00:26:59,279 --> 00:27:00,400
and cannot eat sweets.

492
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:02,200
So these pastries

493
00:27:02,319 --> 00:27:04,119
were specially remade.

494
00:27:04,599 --> 00:27:06,240
A separate portion was made for Mother,

495
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:08,759
and no sugar was added.

496
00:27:09,119 --> 00:27:11,039
Only licorice and dates

497
00:27:11,319 --> 00:27:12,000
were used for flavor.

498
00:27:12,240 --> 00:27:13,240
I also asked Mother's

499
00:27:13,359 --> 00:27:14,640
usual physician

500
00:27:14,759 --> 00:27:15,559
to examine them.

501
00:27:15,920 --> 00:27:17,559
He said these pastries could be eaten.

502
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:19,240
Only then did I send them over.

503
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:23,799
It is kind of your grandmother to remember.

504
00:27:25,599 --> 00:27:27,240
Since such care was taken,

505
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:29,400
I must try them.

506
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,039
Not bad.

507
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,279
As long as Mother likes them.

508
00:27:39,079 --> 00:27:41,440
I also have a presumptuous request.

509
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:44,000
My shop Linxia House

510
00:27:44,119 --> 00:27:45,759
is still short of staff.

511
00:27:46,279 --> 00:27:48,119
I heard Mother's maiden family

512
00:27:48,319 --> 00:27:49,160
is a great clan.

513
00:27:49,519 --> 00:27:52,119
If Mother could recommend a few people,

514
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:54,279
you would be helping me greatly.

515
00:27:54,519 --> 00:27:56,000
So that's it.

516
00:27:58,759 --> 00:28:00,319
Mother, please rest assured.

517
00:28:00,839 --> 00:28:02,319
Whoever Mother recommends

518
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:03,440
shall be treated fairly

519
00:28:03,559 --> 00:28:05,359
in wages.

520
00:28:07,039 --> 00:28:08,039
Very well.

521
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:10,680
Tomorrow I'll write home.

522
00:28:12,079 --> 00:28:13,319
Jinzhao is no simple woman.

523
00:28:13,319 --> 00:28:14,599
Ask if they have someone

524
00:28:15,079 --> 00:28:16,079
- She knows Mother
- to spare

525
00:28:16,079 --> 00:28:17,200
- favors her maiden kin,
- for your business.

526
00:28:17,759 --> 00:28:19,119
yet turns even that

527
00:28:19,119 --> 00:28:20,160
into a means to please Mother.

528
00:28:20,599 --> 00:28:21,759
She

529
00:28:21,759 --> 00:28:22,680
was abducted.
- Such a flagrant mistake
- Since

530
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:24,640
you have business to attend to,
will be pardoned like this?

531
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:28,440
your daily morning and evening greetings

532
00:28:28,839 --> 00:28:30,000
can be waived too.

533
00:28:30,279 --> 00:28:30,960
Yes.

534
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,319
Since Jinzhao's Linxia House

535
00:28:34,759 --> 00:28:36,799
will only receive female guests,

536
00:28:37,359 --> 00:28:38,759
I suppose from now on,

537
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,119
the Grand Secretaries' wives

538
00:28:40,119 --> 00:28:41,759
will be regular guests there.

539
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,200
The ladies of Wenyuan Pavilion

540
00:28:44,519 --> 00:28:45,680
hold a tea gathering

541
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:46,759
on the seventh of every month.

542
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,839
Now that Jinzhao

543
00:28:48,839 --> 00:28:50,160
is also a Grand Secretary's wife,

544
00:28:50,559 --> 00:28:52,559
the day after tomorrow is the seventh.

545
00:28:53,519 --> 00:28:54,839
Then, Jinzhao,

546
00:28:55,119 --> 00:28:56,880
have you already received an invitation?

547
00:28:58,400 --> 00:29:00,799
I have never heard of this tea gathering.

548
00:29:03,359 --> 00:29:05,640
It's normal not to receive one.

549
00:29:06,079 --> 00:29:07,559
After all, you are still young.

550
00:29:07,839 --> 00:29:10,160
Those ladies are older than you,

551
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:12,519
and are born to noble houses.

552
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:14,799
Naturally,

553
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:16,680
you have little to talk about with them.

554
00:29:19,559 --> 00:29:20,279
Yes.

555
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:27,599
Old Madam.

556
00:29:28,039 --> 00:29:28,799
Third Madam.

557
00:29:30,359 --> 00:29:31,400
The household of Chancellor Wang

558
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,839
just sent an invitation.

559
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,599
They invite Third Madam

560
00:29:34,839 --> 00:29:36,160
to tea the day after tomorrow.

561
00:29:39,759 --> 00:29:40,480
I understand.

562
00:29:56,119 --> 00:29:57,079
How is your injury?

563
00:30:01,079 --> 00:30:01,880
I'm all right now.

564
00:30:02,599 --> 00:30:03,559
Have they caught

565
00:30:03,759 --> 00:30:04,559
the mastermind?

566
00:30:06,119 --> 00:30:07,039
Mr. Chen is still checking.

567
00:30:07,279 --> 00:30:08,359
I haven't asked much.

568
00:30:10,599 --> 00:30:11,559
You were truly lucky this time.

569
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:13,559
Had Third Uncle been any later,

570
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:15,960
you might already

571
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:17,519
have met with harm.

572
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:21,559
I truly never expected

573
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,599
you would choose to marry him.

574
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,599
Was it because of his rank and power?

575
00:30:28,559 --> 00:30:29,559
But in my heart,

576
00:30:30,480 --> 00:30:31,759
you should not be that kind of person.

577
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,559
I don't know what you mean.

578
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:34,960
I have to go.
I'll leave first.

579
00:30:37,039 --> 00:30:37,759
You are that unwilling
to speak with me?

580
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,319
How could you say that?

581
00:30:43,720 --> 00:30:45,119
I am only in a hurry to go out.

582
00:30:45,799 --> 00:30:46,319
By the way,

583
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,720
since I have married Mr. Chen,

584
00:30:49,039 --> 00:30:50,640
you should call me Aunt Chen.

585
00:31:02,799 --> 00:31:03,200
You...

586
00:31:06,319 --> 00:31:06,960
Forgive me.

587
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:09,319
I stepped on it by accident.

588
00:31:11,759 --> 00:31:12,400
Forget it.

589
00:31:12,759 --> 00:31:13,519
I don't want it.

590
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:28,759
Young master.

591
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,079
Let's go back.

592
00:31:31,519 --> 00:31:32,079
Tomorrow,

593
00:31:32,799 --> 00:31:33,720
take this earring

594
00:31:34,119 --> 00:31:34,759
to the silver shop.

595
00:31:36,119 --> 00:31:37,519
Have them make an identical pair.

596
00:31:38,279 --> 00:31:39,279
Send it to Gu Jinzhao.

597
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:40,079
Young master,

598
00:31:40,279 --> 00:31:41,559
you must not do this.

599
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:43,200
We have already

600
00:31:43,799 --> 00:31:45,000
made too many mistakes.

601
00:31:45,079 --> 00:31:46,160
If I tell you to go, then go.

602
00:31:47,799 --> 00:31:48,559
For her,

603
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:49,640
I've already gone so far...

604
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,519
Why can she still act

605
00:31:59,519 --> 00:32:00,359
as if nothing happened?

606
00:32:03,839 --> 00:32:05,559
So there really is such a tea gathering.

607
00:32:07,559 --> 00:32:08,160
What?
You want to go?

608
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,119
You don't want me to?

609
00:32:11,319 --> 00:32:12,119
Of course not.

610
00:32:13,119 --> 00:32:14,519
I'm afraid the Wangs

611
00:32:15,319 --> 00:32:16,279
will plot against you.

612
00:32:17,799 --> 00:32:19,519
Is it connected

613
00:32:19,720 --> 00:32:20,480
to last time's roadblock?
Yes.

614
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:23,720
What a man is

615
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:24,799
this Wang Xuanfan?

616
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:26,799
Last time, in the disaster grain case,

617
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:27,440
he deliberately

618
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:28,519
threw dirty water on you

619
00:32:28,759 --> 00:32:29,559
and had you jailed.

620
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:32,400
Why is he here again?

621
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:35,279
Since last time,

622
00:32:35,599 --> 00:32:36,759
I told my teacher

623
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:38,799
that if we want land equalization across the realm,

624
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,680
we must start with ourselves.

625
00:32:42,039 --> 00:32:42,799
Grand Secretaries

626
00:32:43,319 --> 00:32:44,960
must take the lead in auditing their own households

627
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,640
and clear their own taxes.

628
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:47,279
Only then can they

629
00:32:47,279 --> 00:32:48,559
to audit lower officials.

630
00:32:48,759 --> 00:32:49,640
When lower officials

631
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:50,920
have cleared their own households,

632
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,000
then audit the gentry and wealthy households.

633
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:54,920
So my teacher required

634
00:32:55,319 --> 00:32:56,680
officials of the third rank and above

635
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:58,880
to examine themselves and return what was owed.

636
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,559
Wang Xuanfan is

637
00:33:00,559 --> 00:33:01,640
a famed Daming landowner.

638
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:02,920
In one go, he disgorged

639
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,039
tens of thousands of taels.

640
00:33:08,359 --> 00:33:09,200
No wonder.

641
00:33:09,319 --> 00:33:11,240
Take his livelihood, you kill his parents.

642
00:33:11,839 --> 00:33:12,839
No wonder he hates you.

643
00:33:15,519 --> 00:33:16,400
So

644
00:33:17,119 --> 00:33:18,279
he devised a method

645
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:20,200
to incite the scholars to make trouble for me.

646
00:33:20,519 --> 00:33:21,599
No matter what the result,

647
00:33:22,319 --> 00:33:23,319
he wanted to pin the charge

648
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,720
of unfair land equalization

649
00:33:25,279 --> 00:33:26,400
on my head.

650
00:33:27,599 --> 00:33:29,599
A stain is what Grand Secretaries fear most.

651
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,359
Once a stain like this

652
00:33:31,799 --> 00:33:33,359
is seized upon,

653
00:33:33,559 --> 00:33:34,559
I very well might

654
00:33:35,319 --> 00:33:36,680
be sent home under disgrace.

655
00:33:40,519 --> 00:33:41,640
So that is it.

656
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:54,200
The invitation has reached Chen Manor.

657
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,319
Mrs. Chen said
she will come.

658
00:33:57,720 --> 00:33:58,839
Which Chen Manor?

659
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,400
Chen Yanyun's.

660
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:04,880
The tea gathering is the day after tomorrow.

661
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:06,519
I sent for that Gu Jinzhao.

662
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,920
Why invite her?

663
00:34:08,119 --> 00:34:09,280
Have you nothing better to do?

664
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:12,000
She is also a Grand Secretary's wife.

665
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:14,239
Shouldn't she be invited to the tea gathering?

666
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:15,559
Did someone

667
00:34:15,559 --> 00:34:16,639
make you angry somewhere?

668
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:18,119
You're taking it out on me.

669
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:20,960
Where else could I be angered?

670
00:34:21,639 --> 00:34:22,559
Isn't this all because of

671
00:34:22,559 --> 00:34:23,880
your rotten idea?

672
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,079
Fine, fine, fine. All of you,

673
00:34:28,079 --> 00:34:28,880
all leave.

674
00:34:39,519 --> 00:34:40,960
You had me stir up those scholars

675
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:42,400
to block Chen Yanyun's carriage

676
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:43,519
and cry, 'Unfair reform!'

677
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,519
And what happened?
Now I've dragged myself

678
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:46,320
right into it.

679
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:48,440
Chen Yanyun knows.

680
00:34:49,119 --> 00:34:50,360
Even if he does, no need to fear.

681
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:51,960
Those scholars

682
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,159
were not wrong to begin with.

683
00:34:54,079 --> 00:34:56,440
This land equalization is unfair.

684
00:34:56,679 --> 00:34:58,639
You know nothing of this!

685
00:34:58,960 --> 00:35:00,039
Do you know what slogan

686
00:35:00,039 --> 00:35:01,400
those scholars are shouting now?

687
00:35:01,880 --> 00:35:03,599
Audit the imperial estates.

688
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:05,920
Count His Majesty's private property.

689
00:35:06,199 --> 00:35:06,880
I told them

690
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:08,239
to shout that land equalization is unfair.

691
00:35:08,320 --> 00:35:09,000
I never told them

692
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,880
to audit His Majesty's land!

693
00:35:11,679 --> 00:35:13,280
Then Fu Hailian scolded you?

694
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:14,079
What else?

695
00:35:15,239 --> 00:35:15,920
Before Chen Yanyun,

696
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:17,199
he gave me a thorough dressing-down.

697
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:18,880
And you, of all people,

698
00:35:19,199 --> 00:35:20,639
still invited Gu Jinzhao.

699
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:22,280
Aren't you ashamed?

700
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:24,719
What do I have to be ashamed of?

701
00:35:25,199 --> 00:35:26,719
You're the one who's ashamed, all right?

702
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:29,280
Since this time

703
00:35:29,519 --> 00:35:30,920
you suffered at Chen Yanyun's hands,

704
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:34,159
all the more I must invite Gu Jinzhao.

705
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:34,880
No.

706
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,280
You want to go that badly?

707
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:55,400
You saw through me.

708
00:36:00,039 --> 00:36:01,679
I'm afraid they'll plot against you.

709
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:04,760
I'm not so easy to bully.

710
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,119
True.

711
00:36:07,599 --> 00:36:08,639
I'm even more afraid

712
00:36:09,159 --> 00:36:10,519
you'll clash with them.

713
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:11,519
What?

714
00:36:11,639 --> 00:36:13,079
Are you afraid you can't protect me?

715
00:36:16,360 --> 00:36:17,519
Trying to provoke me?

716
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:19,159
I am a Grand Secretary.

717
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:21,119
Though my seniority is shallow,

718
00:36:21,639 --> 00:36:23,440
protecting you is more than enough.

719
00:36:24,639 --> 00:36:25,800
Then that's settled.

720
00:36:27,199 --> 00:36:28,760
I want to attend the tea gathering

721
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:30,360
not for my own amusement,

722
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:31,639
but because

723
00:36:31,639 --> 00:36:33,320
it is the Grand Secretaries' wives' tea gathering.

724
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,079
If I don't go,

725
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:37,320
am I not cutting myself off from that circle?

726
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,840
That would embarrass you too.

727
00:36:41,519 --> 00:36:42,400
I know.

728
00:36:44,239 --> 00:36:45,519
These Grand Secretaries' wives

729
00:36:45,639 --> 00:36:46,880
are all senior to me.

730
00:36:47,679 --> 00:36:48,800
Even Mrs. Shen

731
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:50,360
comes from a noble family

732
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:52,000
with deep learning.

733
00:36:52,920 --> 00:36:53,760
Don't worry.

734
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:55,320
I won't offend them.

735
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:57,599
All right.

736
00:36:58,639 --> 00:37:00,760
Then I'll ask around for you

737
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:02,840
about these ladies:

738
00:37:03,159 --> 00:37:04,440
what their temperaments are

739
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:06,039
and what they like.

740
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:08,519
Where would you ask?

741
00:37:08,679 --> 00:37:10,320
They are all noble ladies of the capital.

742
00:37:11,119 --> 00:37:12,440
If people find out,

743
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:13,840
they'll mock you behind your back.

744
00:37:15,159 --> 00:37:16,320
I have my own ways.

745
00:38:02,199 --> 00:38:03,840
Mrs. Chen, this way please.

746
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:14,280
Mrs. Fu.

747
00:38:16,079 --> 00:38:17,079
Mrs. Wang.

748
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,559
Mrs. Yao.

749
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,159
Mrs. He.

750
00:38:23,519 --> 00:38:24,880
Greetings, ladies.

751
00:38:50,039 --> 00:38:51,280
Greetings, Mrs. Chen.

752
00:38:51,519 --> 00:38:52,360
Please sit.

753
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:55,639
Miss Qingpu.

754
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:57,519
Please come this way to rest.

755
00:39:11,519 --> 00:39:12,760
Look at this new bride.

756
00:39:13,400 --> 00:39:14,960
Her pearls and jade are so plain,

757
00:39:15,079 --> 00:39:16,360
yet she looks so fresh and pretty.

758
00:39:16,840 --> 00:39:18,360
Her skin is so dewy.

759
00:39:18,679 --> 00:39:20,079
Youth is such a fine thing.

760
00:39:20,559 --> 00:39:21,880
Mrs. He, you flatter me.

761
00:39:22,119 --> 00:39:22,800
I dare not accept it.

762
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,519
If we speak of beauty,

763
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:26,159
all of you ladies

764
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,679
are far more elegant and peerless.

765
00:39:28,239 --> 00:39:29,079
I merely

766
00:39:29,239 --> 00:39:30,800
was born a little later.

767
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:34,079
By the way,

768
00:39:34,679 --> 00:39:35,360
today

769
00:39:35,519 --> 00:39:37,199
is my first time at this tea gathering.

770
00:39:37,559 --> 00:39:38,760
I prepared gifts

771
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:39,760
for all of you ladies.

772
00:39:42,159 --> 00:39:43,559
Please, no gifts.

773
00:39:44,119 --> 00:39:45,400
This is a tea gathering,

774
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:46,599
not some place outside

775
00:39:46,599 --> 00:39:48,360
to curry favor and do business.

776
00:39:49,360 --> 00:39:51,320
The husbands of those seated here

777
00:39:51,679 --> 00:39:52,920
are either Grand Secretaries

778
00:39:53,199 --> 00:39:54,639
or important court ministers.

779
00:39:55,360 --> 00:39:56,000
We ourselves

780
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:57,880
also bear imperial titles.

781
00:39:58,159 --> 00:39:59,840
If we start exchanging gifts,

782
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:01,079
once word spreads,

783
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:03,400
at best, we invite ridicule;

784
00:40:03,760 --> 00:40:06,199
at worst, we give people a handle against us.

785
00:40:08,079 --> 00:40:09,880
When Mrs. Fu set this rule,

786
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:11,960
I thought she worried too much.

787
00:40:12,199 --> 00:40:13,199
I didn't expect

788
00:40:13,400 --> 00:40:15,360
someone would truly bring gifts.

789
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,679
I was rash.

790
00:40:19,119 --> 00:40:20,880
This is my first tea gathering.

791
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,960
I thought courtesy could not offend.

792
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:24,480
I did not know

793
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,400
such customs applied.

794
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:26,880
The fault is mine.

795
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:29,079
When Mrs. Wang's invitation arrived,

796
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:30,239
I set about preparing gifts.

797
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:31,519
I ought to have

798
00:40:31,679 --> 00:40:33,400
sought Mrs. Wang's guidance first.

799
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:37,960
Since the invitation came from you,

800
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:41,039
a word of guidance was surely in order.

801
00:40:42,719 --> 00:40:43,360
Yes.

802
00:40:44,039 --> 00:40:45,320
It was my oversight.

803
00:40:47,639 --> 00:40:48,960
Is everyone here?

804
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:49,840
Yes.

805
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,840
The garden is ready.

806
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:53,360
Let's all go together.

807
00:41:03,199 --> 00:41:03,960
It's nothing serious.
Don't worry.

808
00:41:15,519 --> 00:41:16,519
I hear

809
00:41:16,840 --> 00:41:18,679
the post of Left Vice Minister of Rites is vacant.

810
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:20,079
Court nominations were held twice,

811
00:41:20,079 --> 00:41:21,360
yet no choice was made.

812
00:41:23,199 --> 00:41:24,320
In my view,

813
00:41:25,519 --> 00:41:27,880
Lord Zeng Ruoyu

814
00:41:28,119 --> 00:41:29,320
is steady in character

815
00:41:29,760 --> 00:41:31,719
and a renowned great scholar.

816
00:41:32,039 --> 00:41:33,559
He fits the post perfectly.

817
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,360
Mrs. Yao,

818
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:36,639
what do you think?

819
00:41:40,360 --> 00:41:41,440
My husband

820
00:41:41,519 --> 00:41:43,559
has praised Lord Zeng several times too.

821
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:45,800
This round of nominations

822
00:41:46,440 --> 00:41:48,519
will most likely favor Lord Zeng.

823
00:41:49,639 --> 00:41:50,519
Good.

824
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,599
My husband said

825
00:41:55,239 --> 00:41:57,199
Wenyuan Pavilion needs Pavilion Secretaries.

826
00:41:58,519 --> 00:42:00,199
I remember you have a nephew

827
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:02,639
who is a Jinshi from Jingning 35.

828
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,599
Perhaps put his name forward.

829
00:42:06,639 --> 00:42:08,320
Then on behalf of my nephew,

830
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:09,159
I thank you, Madam.

831
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,199
Mrs. Shen.

832
00:42:19,159 --> 00:42:19,840
You seem

833
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:21,320
a little distracted today.

834
00:42:22,960 --> 00:42:23,599
Madam.

835
00:42:27,119 --> 00:42:27,679
You know

836
00:42:27,679 --> 00:42:29,119
my husband's temper.

837
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:30,719
It comes fast and goes fast.

838
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:32,880
When you return, tell Keqian

839
00:42:33,239 --> 00:42:34,599
he need not worry too much.

840
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,519
He only loses his temper like that

841
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,960
with those he trusts.

842
00:42:38,519 --> 00:42:39,320
I understand.

843
00:42:39,559 --> 00:42:40,519
Thank you, Madam.

844
00:42:46,920 --> 00:42:48,079
Let me go! Let me go!

845
00:42:48,079 --> 00:42:49,360
Let me go, all of you! Let me go!

846
00:42:49,599 --> 00:42:50,960
I'm a court official! Let me go!

847
00:42:51,079 --> 00:42:51,920
Have you no law in your eyes? Let go!

848
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:53,039
Is there no justice left?

849
00:42:53,280 --> 00:42:54,360
Let me go!

850
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:56,920
Reporting to the Commander,

851
00:42:57,119 --> 00:42:58,519
At the West City inn,

852
00:42:58,719 --> 00:43:00,119
I seized An Deyu and his wife.

853
00:43:00,440 --> 00:43:01,480
One official seal was found.

854
00:43:02,639 --> 00:43:03,719
Please inspect it, sir.

855
00:43:04,440 --> 00:43:05,440
An imperial warrant?

856
00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:07,159
The Three Judicial Offices are still reviewing it.

857
00:43:07,480 --> 00:43:08,920
How could His Majesty issue such an edict?

858
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:20,679
Ye Xian.

859
00:43:20,960 --> 00:43:22,679
Investigating Censor of the Censorate.

860
00:43:23,599 --> 00:43:24,360
An Deyu.

861
00:43:24,559 --> 00:43:26,519
You sold offices, neglected duty, and corrupted the law.

862
00:43:27,159 --> 00:43:28,079
By imperial command,

863
00:43:28,639 --> 00:43:29,719
take him to the Imperial Prison.

864
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:31,800
Lies!

865
00:43:32,239 --> 00:43:33,440
You are slandering me!

866
00:43:34,519 --> 00:43:35,199
My lord.
